(80513, 10508, 7269, 7, '18 People', '', '2014-09-19 00:00:00', 2000, 25, 0, 7, '', 'Eighteen People are painting your whole life\nYou hear the stairs are creaking\nMy lungs are quickly leaking\n\nThe nasty tiny monsters coming from the floor\nI give them bitter biscuits\nTook from my brother''s pocket\n\nI got electric light, bring something from the dark into your eyes\nI got electric light, to show you every corner inside your mind\n\n\n\nA crippled postman put a letter on my door\nIt''s from one of the eighteen\nMy pants are always thinking\n\nLook inside the windows standing on your toes\nBut it shows me nothing\nLike a deep black mirror\n\nLight falls on the floor, shades are running into my skin\nSinging a song in the darkness, to color my mind\nLight falls on the floor, shades are running into my skin\nSinging a song in the darkness, to color my mind\nLight falls on the floor, shades are running into my skin\nSinging a song in the darkness, to color my mind\nLight falls on the floor, shades are running into my skin\nSinging a song in the darkness, to color my mind\n\nSleep in a tragic night, to share a dream with eighteen different minds\nWake by a solid light, the eighteen people back in the same time', 242, '', '', '', '', 'Sony Music', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-09-18 19:45:45', '2015-03-12 14:09:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(80514, 10508, 7269, 8, '紅色河流', '', '2014-09-19 00:00:00', 2000, 25, 0, 7, '', '有一條河流載著我溶解的身體\n影子們跟著人群 爬上了階梯\n影子們交換一些日常的秘密\n秘密們隨著日落 散開在黑暗裡\n\n有一條河流載著我溶解的身體\n黑暗中有個聲音 急促的呼吸\n灰塵們飄在空中 吸進了身體\n跟著那血液流動 聚集到心臟裡\n\n\n\n誰攪拌我的白晝和夜晚\n帶著我 來回的折返 每個呼吸間\n誰打開我 意識前紅色們\n載著我 流出了身體 接著又沈睡\n\n終於僵硬的身體 碎滿地 被河流帶走！\n\n\n\n有一條河流載著我溶解的身體\n巨大的心跳搖動 房子裡的空氣\n房子們蓋在一片 絕望的土地\n土地上流過是我 溶解後的身體...\n\n\n\n誰攪拌我的白晝和夜晚\n帶著我 來回的折返 每個呼吸間\n誰打開我 意識前紅色們\n載著我 流出了身體 接著又沈睡\n\n終於僵硬的身體 碎滿地 被河流帶走！', 269, '', '', '', '', 'Sony Music', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-09-18 19:47:05', '2015-03-12 14:09:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
